{"tid":490272,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日炒乜輪】有人今早低位撈騰訊牛 4萬變52萬！","createTime":"2017-12-05T12:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T11:06:59.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5cafca7e7aff60e263a7e6cf13aeaf15b5d00d8","tid":490272,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"今早開市騰訊（700）繼續屠牛，最低跌至377.2元，共有29隻牛證打靶，涉及約9億份街貨被收回。重貨牛證被殺晒後，騰訊股價報復性反彈，一度從低位急彈半成，全日倒升0.88%，收報388.4元。今早有4隻騰訊牛證收回價為376.98元，分別為69255、69167、68927、69047，距離被打只差一線。逃出生天後，該4隻騰訊牛證爆炸式上升，以今日高位計，一度由低位爆升逾10倍！<br />\n<br />\n交易資料顯示，有炒家今早低位大手撈生死只差一線的騰訊牛證。在9點34分，有一宗大手買賣以0.02元價位買入195萬股騰訊牛證（69047），耗資3萬9千元，假設今日倘未沽出，以高位0.295元計，一度翻至57.5萬元，勁賺13.7倍；若以收市價0.212元計，亦升了9.6倍，賺37萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171204/57539068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F57539068&d=kUkaD7vI9fW7Nx7zQK%2Ff3k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7dfbea48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F57539068&h=f2124876\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171204/57539068</a>"},{"pid":"d91d30e6a3343bc529b99e3a9b91d673cc2ef263","tid":490272,"uid":14557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"打曬"},{"pid":"107c7338444d911fa0e889e2aeca30888e681ec0","tid":490272,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42825a81cb28cfb7714c60bd4649fde60a135b81","tid":490272,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"十點就打左把 52萬？5個2都未必有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi